<HL>
   Huffy Says Sales
   Of Mountain Bikes
   Pushing Up Profit
   ----
   By Gabriella Stern
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/03/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6B
</SO>
<CO>
   HUF
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
<IN>
DOW JONES INTERVIEW (CEO)
ENTERTAINMENT AND LEISURE (ENT)
RECREATION, ENTERTAINMENT, TOYS, MOVIES, PHOTOGRAPHY (REC)
LEISURE TIME SERVICES AND PRODUCTS (REQ)
</IN>
<NS>
EXCLUSIVE INTERVIEW WITH CHIEF EXECUTIVES (CEO)
